/www.nme.com/news/music/fans-react-to-rush-for-black-sabbath-final-gig-tickets-3838021">许多球迷感到沮丧，试图确保门票</a>。有些人还批评了高<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-sabbaths-final-gig-in-birmingham-ticket-prices-revealed-3836924">票价</a>- 尽管所有利润都在帕金森氏菌，伯明翰儿童医院和橡子儿童临终关怀中平均分配。虽然其他人很高兴他们设法获得了演出的门票。</p><p>同时，安息日成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tony-iommi-shares-emotional-statement-on-final-black-sabbath-show-what-we-created-together-was-bigger-than-any-one-of-us-3835182">Iommi</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-geezer-butler-share-first-statement-on-black-sabbaths-final-gig-3835492">Butler</a>最近都分享了即将在社交媒体上举行的聚会的陈述。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/classic-era-ozzy-osbourne-bassist-bob-daisley-speaks-out-on-being-snubbed-from-final-gig-it-could-be-an-embarrassment-but-well-see-3836634">鲍勃·戴斯利（Bob Daisley）是经典时代奥兹（Ozzy）贝斯手 - 还谈到没有被邀请参加乐队的最后一场演出</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-sabbaths-2013-concert-film-live-gathered-in-their-masses-is-streaming-for-free-on-youtube-3840613">Black Sabbath的2013年音乐会电影“ Live…聚集在他们的群众中”在</a><a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上免费出现在YouTube上。</p> ;
