 Stage&#39; world tour, featuring concerts in the US and Asia. The tour will kick off with a three-night concert running from February 28 to March 2 at Seoul&#39;s KSPO Dome, before he bring his tour to 14 more cities on both continents, all with two nights each.</p><h2> jisoo </h2><figure id="attachment_3832131" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3832131" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3832131" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/blackpink-jisoo-amortage-mini-album-solo-debut-february-2025-valentines.jpg" alt="blackpink jisoo amortage mini album solo debut february 2025 valentines" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/blackpink-jisoo-amortage-mini-album-solo-debut-february-2025-valentines.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/blackpink-jisoo-amortage-mini-album-solo-debut-february-2025-valentines-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/blackpink-jisoo-amortage-mini-album-solo-debut-february-2025-valentines-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/blackpink-jisoo-amortage-mini-album-solo-debut-february-2025-valentines-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/blackpink-jisoo-amortage-mini-album-solo-debut-february-2025-valentines-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/blackpink-jisoo-amortage-mini-album-solo-debut-february-2025-valentines-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3832131" class="wp-caption-text"> BLACKPINK&#39;s Jisoo. Credit: Taylor Hill/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> <strong>2025 &#39;Lights, Love, Action!&#39; Asia tour – Tokyo, Manila, Bangkok, Macau, Taipei, Hong Kong and Hanoi</strong></p><p> <strong>2025年3月<br /></strong>Friday 14 – Manila, the Philippines, Smart Araneta Coliseum<br /> Saturday 15 – Bangkok, Thai