a> recently <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-killers-brandon-flowers-interview-rebel-diamonds-tour-new-album-solo-band-hot-fuss-3560425">revealed to <em>NME</em> that he&#39;s working on his third solo album</a> .</p><p> He said: “I&#39;m making a solo record right now!我差点把它包裹起来。这是不同的。 I feel like it embodies a little bit of my first two solo records, but obviously there&#39;s so much more living that I&#39;ve done in the seven years since my last effort. I&#39;ve got a lot more insight and things that I&#39;ve absorbed. I&#39;m really loving how it&#39;s turning out.”</p><p> As for a potential new Killers record, Flowers said it is likely to continue in the same vein as their last album 2021&#39;s &#39; <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-killers-pressure-machine-review-3017509">Pressure Machine</a> &#39;.</p><p> He said: “I realised that the vehicle that I want to ride in had less synthesisers and less laser beams! I&#39;m trying to figure that out. It&#39;s not uncommon; we&#39;ve made records like &#39; <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/the-killers-sams-town-reappraised-4892">Sam&#39;s Town</a> &#39; [2006], &#39; <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-the-killers-13685-323828">Battle Born</a> &#39; [2012] and definitely &#39;Pressure Machine&#39; [2021] where there&#39;s less presence of that kind of sound. I&#39;m not disparaging that sound – a lot of that music has shaped who I am – but as I get older I want to be authentic to who I am and how I&#39;m feeling. I have to follow that, and I just feel like that&#39;s leading more towards guitar music, rock n&#39; roll and Americana music.” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="The Killers on showing the Euro semi-finals at their gig and the legacy of ‘Mr Brightside’" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VgxSQDqvUQ0?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> As for where the next record is going lyrically, Flowers added: “Right now, I&#39;ve been gravitating towards relationships and singing about what it takes for people to really make it, while still having empathy for the things that people go through that break them and trying to work through that.每当我进入这种领土时，它都会通过意识到使它们起作用以及我需要做的东西来使我在自己的关系中变得更加牢固。 It&#39;s a really important process for me because it makes me a better person.”</p><p> The Killers also recently <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-killers-and-bruce-springsteen-to-release-madison-square-garden-performance-for-record-store-day-2025-3836140">announced that they are releasing their Madison Square Garden performance</a> with <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Bruce-Springsteen">Bruce Springsteen</a> for <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/record-store-day">Record Store Day 2025</a> .</p><p> Titled &#39;The Killers &amp; Bruce Springsteen Encore At The Garden&#39;, the 12″ pressing will be available on April 12 at shops participating in Record Store Day. The tracklist is comprised of the three-song encore the band and the boss <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-bruce-springsteen-join-the-killers-at-madison-square-garden-3320849">performed together on October 1, 2022 at the iconic New York arena</a> .只有5,000次发动机可用。</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-killers-cover-john-fogertys-centerfield-at-innings-festival-2025-3840567">Watch The Killers cover John Fogerty&#39;s &#39;Centerfield&#39; at Innings Festival 2025</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
 Fatboy Slim曾经与总理Keir Starmer上小提琴课https://www.nme.com/news/music/fatboy-slim-once-took-violin-lesson-with-prime-minister-keir-keir-starmer-3840562?u tm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = fatboy-slim-once-once-once-once-took-violin-lessons-with-prime-minister-keir-starmerDamian Jones Sun, 23 Feb 2025 21:55:37 +0000 Music NewsNewsPoliticsDance https://www.nme.com/?p=3840562 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_fatboyslim_keirstarmer_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Fatboy Slim和Keir Starmer" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_fatboyslim_keirstarmer_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_fatboyslim_keirstarmer_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_fatboyslim_keirstarmer_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_fatboyslim_keirstarmer_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_fatboyslim_keirstarmer_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_fatboyslim_keirstarmer_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>诺曼·库克（Norman Cook）和斯泰默（Starmer）去了同一所学校五年</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fatboy-slim-once-took-violin-lessons-with-prime-minister-keir-starmer-3840562">Fatboy后的Slim曾经与总理Keir Starmer上小提琴课，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_fatboyslim_keirstarmer_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Fatboy Slim和Keir Starmer" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_fatboyslim_keirstarmer_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_fatboyslim_keirstarmer_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_fatboyslim_keirstarmer_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_fatboyslim_keirstarmer_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_fatboyslim_keirstarmer_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_fatboyslim_keirstarmer_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fatboy-slim">法夫·斯利姆（Fatboy Slim）</a>回忆起他曾经与总理一起上小提琴课。</p><p> DJ和制片人 - 真实姓名诺曼·库克（Norman Cook）也谈到了他在接受<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/music/2025/feb/23/fatboy-slim-australia-tour-interview"><em>《卫报》（Guardian）</em></a>的新采访中与凯尔·斯泰默（Keir Starmer）一起上了五年。</p><p>他说：“我实际上不记得小提琴课。但是我和凯尔（Keir）在学校上学五年，所以我记得他很好。</p><p> “他在小提琴上一定比我更好，因为我做了大约一个学期。我的父母不再有噪音，所以我想说凯尔更好。”</p><p>他继续说：“有一天你看到电视上的某人然后走了，这很奇怪，&#39;哦，看，是4B的凯尔·斯塔默。”我认为他成为总理是我的一个人。”</p><p>库克还说，他的电话中仍然有自己的电话号码，“他们仍然说话”。 </p><figure style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Fatboy-Slim-performing.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">胖男孩苗条的信用：曼尼·埃尔南德斯/盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>他的最新评论回应了他在<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/does-rock-n-roll-kill-braincells-fatboy-slim-3318190">摇滚乐中杀死脑电池的类似言论吗？</a> 2022年<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/does-rock-n-roll-kill-braincells-fatboy-slim-3318190">对<em>NME</em>的采访</a>。</p><p>当时他还说：“怪异的是，我们有另一个同学，他们总是声称他们将成为英格兰总理，我们相信他，因为他们是班上最大的SWOT。他们没有继续管理它，但是Keir很可能会。但是他当时没有表现出任何政治野心。”</p><p>在其他地方，库克<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fatboy-slim-says-that-hes-lost-his-passion-for-making-music-3825254">最近分享说他失去了“制作音乐的热情”</a> 。</p><p>他当时说：“事实是，除非您绝对对此充满热情，否则您将无法制作音乐，并且从您早上醒来的那一刻起就可以驱动您。”</p><p> “我似乎不再觉得那样了。我觉得DJ和戴上这样的事情（全部回到Minehead Butlin的Weekender），但我对制作音乐的热情失去了一种。”库克（Cook）的最后一张全长专辑是Fatboy Slim是2004年的“ Palookaville”。 2010年，他还发行了他与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-byrne">戴维·伯恩（David Byrne）</a>为音乐剧<em>《爱》（Love Love）</em>创作的配乐。</p><p> “五年来，我试图击败自己，然后走，&#39;你应该这样做&#39;。但是后来我想：“好吧，每个人都喜欢我的DJ，我更喜欢它，所以我会做的。”他承认。 “我希望有一天的激情能回来。”</p><p>库克已经计划在2025年与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-fender">萨姆·芬德（Sam Fender）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/raye">雷（Raye）</a>一起参加<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-raye-and-more-to-headline-2025-f1-british-grand-prix-3839703">一级方程式英国大奖赛（Formula 1 British Grand Prix），</a>并在2025年举行<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendal-calling-2024-line-up-the-prodigy-courteeners-fatboy-slim-kaiser-chiefs-and-more-announced-buy-tickets-3808588">肯德尔（Kendal）召唤</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/latitude-festival-announces-headliners-for-2025-buy-tickets-3806899">纬度节</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fatboy-slim-once-took-violin-lessons-with-prime-minister-keir-starmer-3840562">Fatboy后的Slim曾经与总理Keir Starmer上小提琴课，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
经过多年警告对基层威胁和艺术家的可行性的警告，英国的行为已经退出了全球畅销书排行榜https://www.nme.com/news/music/after-dare-of-warning-of-warnning-of-thereat-to-grassroots-and-artists-viable-viability-uk-acts-acts-have-have-dropped of-lobal-畅销书-3840557？u tm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign =年度对威胁性的对格拉斯根和艺术家 - 武器 - 算法-uk-uk-uk-acts-roppopped-troped-global-therlobal-bess-bess-bessellers-sellers-shart-chart-chartDamian Jones Sun, 23 Feb 2025 21:04:51 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndiePophttps://www.nme.com/?p=3840557 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx-grammys.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Charli XCX" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx-grammys.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx-grammys-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx-grammys-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx-grammys-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx-grammys-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx-grammys-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这是英国20多年来第一次未能列入清单</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/after-years-of-warning-of-threat-to-grassroots-and-artists-viability-uk-acts-have-dropped-out-of-global-best-sellers-chart-3840557">经过多年警告对基层威胁和艺术家的可行性的警告，英国的行为已经退出了全球畅销书排行榜，</a>这是<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>首先出现的。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx-grammys.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Charli XCX" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx-grammys.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx-grammys-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx-grammys-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx-grammys-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx-grammys-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx-grammys-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>英国的表演未能进入2024年全球十大畅销单曲或专辑的全球年度排行榜。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-listid="807" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-albums-2024-3818995"><b>2024年最佳专辑</b></a></li></ul><p>根据<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/c5y23pe2v0vo" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>BBC News的</em></a>国际摄影行业联合会（IFPI）的数字，在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/benson-boone">Benson Boone</a>在Benson Boone宣称拥有“美丽的事物”的第一首歌之后，任何一名名单上都没有本土艺术家，Taylor Swift和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">Taylor Swift</a> &#39;S&#39; <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-the-tortured-poets-department-lyrics-tracklist-3619454">折磨诗人部门</a>&#39;是世界上畅销专辑。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-uk-tour-stadium-london-wembley-hull-music-venue-trust-tickets-3794308">Coldplay</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a>的专辑都不列出这两个列表。排名最高的艺术家是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/artemas">Artemas</a> ，他在全球畅销单曲列表中以“我喜欢您的方式亲吻我的方式”排在第15位。</p><p>这两个列表主要由美国法案（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">Sabrina Carpenter</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kendrick-lamar">Kendrick Lamar）</a>所统治。 </p><figure style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Billie-Eilish.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-Live-Nation-Entertainment.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text"> Billie Eilish.学分：凯文·马祖尔/盖蒂的现场娱乐图像</figcaption></figure><p>以前，自2003年以来，英国的行为每年都出现在前十名中的一个或两个中。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/2025-potential-game-changer-uk-grassroots-music-when-see-action-where-will-money-go-3833218">这是在特色艺术家联盟的大卫·马丁（David Martin）最近指出的</a>是<a href="https://newsroom.spotify.com/2024-12-04/top-songs-artists-podcasts-audiobooks-albums-trends-2024/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Spotify的2024年全球溪流艺术家，他说，越来越多的</a>英国名字越来越缺乏，这表明已经遭受了人才管道的折磨，而不是缺乏才华。</p><p>他告诉<em>NME</em> ：“我并不是说这是世界末日，这是可以解决的，但这应该是英国音乐行业的金丝雀。” “整个生态系统能够共同刺激活动？大型竞技场和发起人需要具有远见。您希望他们这样。</p><p> “我们都应该非常担心。在过去七年中，英国在全球音乐市场中的份额已从17％降至10％。去年，有多少英国艺术家在整个官方排行榜上排名最高？这些应该是该行业的危险信号。如果您希望场地做得好，请确保您在其中有表演，并且正在激发新的受众。您希望发起人做得好吗？通过允许艺术家建立新的粉丝群来确保有需求。”</p><p>马丁补充说，英国需要紧急解决围绕<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/music-sales-hit-20-year-high-but-beneath-the-surface-uk-artists-earn-far-below-average-salaries-3827139">流媒体</a>，基层征税， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brexit-touring-europe-strangling-talent-carnets-visa-merch-crew-government-response-summer-2022-3288735">英国脱欧对巡回演出的影响</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-john-backs-paul-mccartney-over-proposed-ai-copyright-law-this-will-dilute-and-threaten-young-artists-earnings-3832051">AI的规定的问题</a>。</p><p>他补充说：“现在，我们需要增长和轻松获胜。” “我认为英国对其潜力的成就却极大地不足。我知道那里的需求以及我们拥有的艺术家的质量。坦率地说，任何说“不再有好音乐”的人都充满了狗屎。那里有很多优秀的音乐，它很难削减，而且在英国的支持下也不是很好。”</p><p>这是在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/government-back-arena-ticket-levy-to-save-grassroots-music-but-urgent-deadline-is-needed-to-prevent-an-even-gloomier-future-3812464">政府最近支持在竞技场及以上征收演出门票的呼吁</a>之后 - 采用“英超联赛模式”，现场直播的顶级层次又回到了生态系统中，以保持人才管道的流动，如他们在足球中做。</p><p>希望现场行业的主要公司能够自愿采取行动，并在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/uk-government-reveals-deadline-for-music-industry-to-respond-to-ticket-levy-to-save-the-grassroots-3820498">三月份进行有意义的决定的截止日期，</a>然后政府重新介入，以根据法律强制执行。</p><p>至于演出空间，音乐场所信托基金会最近报告了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/uk-grassroots-music-venues-touring-collapse-mvt-steve-lamacq-budget-help-3808675">英国的“巡回演出的彻底崩溃”</a> ，已经是来自<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-uk-tour-stadium-london-wembley-hull-music-venue-trust-tickets-3794308">Coldplay</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-announces-uk-european-people-watching-tour-buy-tickets-3803992">Sam Fender</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/katy-perry-announces-lifetimes-2025-uk-tour-donating-to-music-venue-trust-buy-tickets-3813601">Katy Perry</a>等竞技场和体育场巡回演出的票务征收捐款。这也是在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grassroots-music-venues-uk-mvt-report-2024-closing-government-action-needed-kate-nash-parliament-3832257">MVT 2024年的年度报告显示去年每两周丢失的一个场所</a>，近44％的场地亏损，而需要紧急帮助的场地上有近20％的高峰在封闭的边缘。 </p><figure style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/chris-martin-coldplay-1.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text"> Coldplay的Chris Martin。图片来源：John Nacion/Filmmagic</figcaption></figure><p>随着<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/uk-grassroots-music-venues-touring-collapse-mvt-steve-lamacq-budget-help-3808675">政府的实施商业税率和门票的增值税，造成了“严重的障碍”</a> ，以及征税开始采取行动所花费的时间，音乐场所信托基金会首席执行官马克·戴维德（Mark Davyd）表示，英国地点“ 2025年不在森林中”。</p><p>他说：“对于2026年，我要说的是，我们可以看到场地，艺术家和巡回演出巡回赛的光明未来。” “今年仍然很难，但是由于Coldplay，Sam Fender，Katy Perry， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/enter-shikari-announce-2024-uk-arena-tour-in-support-of-music-venue-trust-buy-tickets-3438224">Enter Shikari</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/frank-turner-to-donate-1-from-every-ticket-sale-on-upcoming-uk-tour-to-music-venue-trust-3823161">Frank Turner</a> ，Scruff，Scruff， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/alien-ant-farm-cky-joint-uk-tour-with-1-ticket-levy-for-grassroots-venues-buy-tickets-3752024#:~:text=Last%20May%2C%20the%20band%20shared,support%20them%20throughout%20their%20careers.">Alien Ant Farm</a>的慷慨大方，将提供一些财务支持，我们将尝试和尝试和部署它的方式意味着尽可能多的场所可以到2025年，直到我们期望这种征税开始对场地，艺术家和推动者产生真正的影响。”</p><p>戴维德补充说：“ 2025年将是艰难的一年，没有任何假装，但这是在每个人都了解问题并尽力解决问题的气氛中发生的。”</p><h2 class="ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10"> <b class="ssrcss-1xjjfut-BoldText e5tfeyi3">2024年全球畅销专辑是：</b></h2><div class="ssrcss-1le81vw-ListContainer e5tfeyi0">泰勒·斯威夫特 - &#39;折磨诗人部<br />比利·埃里什（Billie Eilish） - &#39;打我辛苦而柔软<br />Sabrina Carpenter  - “ Short N&#39;Sweet”<br /> Enhypen  - “浪漫：不为人知”<br /> SZA  - &#39;SOS&#39;<br />十七岁 - “溢出感觉”<br />摩根·沃伦（Morgan Wallen） - “一次一件事”<br />十七岁 -  &#39;17就在这里&#39;<br />诺亚·卡汉（Noah Kahan） - “棍子季节”<br />流浪儿童 - “吃”</p><h2 class="ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10"> <b class="ssrcss-1xjjfut-BoldText e5tfeyi3">2024年全球畅销单曲是：</b></h2><div class="ssrcss-1le81vw-ListContainer e5tfeyi0">本森·布恩（Benson Boone） - “美丽的事物”<br /> Sabrina Carpenter  - “浓缩咖啡”<br />泰迪游泳 - “失去控制”<br /> Billie Eilish  - “羽毛鸟”<br /> Shaboozey  - “一首酒吧歌（Tipsy）”<br /> Hozier  - “太甜”<br />帖子马龙 - “我有帮助”（壮举摩根·沃伦）<br />肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar） - “不喜欢我们”<br />泰勒·斯威夫特 - “残酷的夏天”<br />诺亚·卡汉（Noah Kahan） - “棍子季节”</div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/after-years-of-warning-of-threat-to-grassroots-and-artists-viability-uk-acts-have-dropped-out-of-global-best-sellers-chart-3840557">经过多年警告对基层威胁和艺术家的可行性的警告，英国的行为已经退出了全球畅销书排行榜，</a>这是<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>首先出现的。</p> ;
